   is stable in many of the binary compounds studied so far, a distortion
   of the rocksalt structure which hay been named Cmcm after its space
   group. Our theoretical study focuses on this novel and rather general
   phase. We have investigated the instability of the rocksalt cell with
   respect to the distortion leading to Cmcm. The results of our ab initio
